name: Not Enough Space (DoubleCrescent)
description:
Not Enough Space is a Horde Survival game developed in 48 hours for the AIE September 2022 Game Jam.

Control an agile space fighter and defend yourselved against increasingly deadly hordes of alien ships. Level up to earn new weapons or upgrade existing ones. How long can you survive in the depths of open space?

Developers: Team Whirlwind
Programmers: Zaydan Bickley, Paul Moustrides
Designers: Cayce Del Gaudio, Joshua Lehmann
